You have a twisted soul! Twisted Souls are never
bad, and actually, are a rarity amongst souls.
These souls are a little combination of
everything, with always a little of their own
chaos to add. Twisted Souls are kind, loving,
weird, zany, temperamental, and very talented.
They have their own firm opinion, and can at
one time be very outspoken and passionate, and
the other time shy and feeling insignificant.
Twisted Souls have good senses of Humor and
other times can be a bore. You can act quite
intelligent at one time, and grasp concepts
easily, while other times they can find it
difficult to understand. Twisted Souls are
always very fun and Kind, and can be party
animals. But, if you love someone, youre
serious about it, intense, and forever loyal.
Congratulations-the world should have more like
you.

i hate my house. i hate my room. i hate my kitchen. i hate my yard. i hate my street. i hate this town. i hate this state. i hate this country. i hate my mom. i hate my dad. i hate my family. i hate my school. i hate my hair. i hate my fingers. i hate my toes. i hate my past. i hate my present. i hate my future. i hate myself. i hate my age. i hate my computer. i hate my pictures. i hate my curfew. and most of all i hate my life.

it's not my fault all my friends r older than me. it's your fault for having me so late in life. and, come on, a 7 year olds curfew is 8:30, not a 13 year old! im sorry you didn't have a life when you were 13, but i try to. and the night after i get un-grounded, i want to go hang out with my friends. and be out after 8:30! you shouldn't care if im in a car with a teen driver or not! just be happy i have friends! because i'm probably not going to for very much longer. im not going to have a  life for very much longer.

you have no idea how pissed off i am right now. i dont even want to talk about wat happened. bottom line, one of my friends cant be my friend any more because my dad decided to be a jack-ass, i have a curfew of fucking 8:30, and i really dont want to be here right now. i dont want to be living right now. i want everything and everyone to just go away. especially my parents.
